name: Simulation cloud 1
description:
This interactive scene is 3D snapshot of a real-time 3D particle simulation implemented in Three.js, where various force fields shape an initial particle cloud (find more info at www.lumicles.xyz). 

Check the help icon to learn how to control the orbital & drone cameras to navigate through the cloud and change the visualization settings.
